/** Readme **/

1) create the database as regista(eg) in your hosting server

2) open the follwing folder and open regista.sql file copy the content or upload the file 
in your phpmyadmin under the regista database it will create the tables
 -> regista\db\regista.sql

3) open the follwing folder and open database.php file to change the database user name, password 
and given db name as per you DB settings.

regista\application\config\database.php

$db['default']['hostname'] = 'localhost';
$db['default']['username'] = 'root';
$db['default']['password'] = '';
$db['default']['database'] = 'regista';

4) upload the files to your hosting server using ftp in the root folder.

